lead_paragraph: Shashank Manohar resigned as President of the powerful Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI) on Tuesday eyeing a second term as chief of the sport's global governing body.

headline.print_headline: Manohar Quits as Indian Board Chief Ahead of ICC Election
